When Breath Becomes Air|Paul Kalanithi|Random House|A memoir by a physician who received a diagnosis of Stage IV lung cancer at the age of 36.
The Subtle Art Of Not Giving A F*Ck|Mark Manson|HarperOne/HarperCollins|A blogger argues that we should stop striving to be positive at all times and instead become better at handling adversity.
The Whole30 Cookbook|Melissa Hartwig|Houghton Mifflin Harcourt|Recipes for the Whole30 program of nonprocessed whole foods and no grains, dairy or sugar.
The Lose Your Belly Diet|Travis Stork|Ghost Mountain|The doctor and talk-show host promotes an eating plan that includes improving "gut health."
The Gene|Siddhartha Mukherjee|Scribner|An overview of the history and science of genetics by the Pulitzer Prize-winning author of “The Emperor of All Maladies.”
Medical Medium Life-Changing Foods|Anthony William|Hay House|Unconventional advice about 50 foods, the symptoms and conditions they can help relieve, and recipes.
Green Smoothies For Life|J J Smith|Atria|A 30-day plan for weight loss that includes recipes for meals and special treats.
The Zero Sugar Diet|David Zinczenko with Stephen Perrine|Ballantine|A 14-day plan for cutting out all sugar and using protein and fiber to slow the absorption of carbohydrates.
10-Day Green Smoothie Cleanse|J J Smith|Atria|Beverages of combined leafy greens and fruits are the basis for a weight loss and health plan.
Being Mortal|Atul Gawande|Metropolitan/Holt|The surgeon and New Yorker writer considers how doctors fail patients at the end of life and how they can do better.
